{"tid":1762130,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)不死J神","createTime":"2019-11-29T11:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T20:01:47.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4695afe3044828d18d5b7f0bc32dbdef6a1373","tid":1762130,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:13:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊~~~死黑警~~~又唔做嘢又唔讀書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=74bd7e5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=e28233c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=8fb9285a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b2/The_Transporter_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb2%2FThe_Transporter_Poster.jpg&h=d7227631&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/f/ff/Warposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Ff%2Fff%2FWarposter.jpg&h=88a79c31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d2/Death_race_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fd%2Fd2%2FDeath_race_poster.jpg&h=45024480&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/90/Mechanic_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F90%2FMechanic_poster.jpg&h=a0cb3255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一家廢棄物回收商「ECO-CORP」，想要把回收來的有毒廢棄物運至烏克蘭丟棄，卻遭到烏克蘭環保部部長斷然拒絕，於是「ECO-CORP」命令槍手約拿&middot;強生綁架了部長的愛女瓦倫蒂娜，想逼部長就範。強生認為自己運送肉票有危險，於是強迫了法蘭克接下了這個任務，並在法蘭克、瓦倫蒂娜手上綁上了炸彈感應手環，只要他們一離開汽車，他們就會被炸死，法蘭克要怎麼帶著瓦倫蒂娜全面封鎖呢？<br />\n<br />\n2.美國聯邦探員傑克克勞佛（傑森史塔森 飾）的搭檔遭到殺手羅格（李連杰 飾）冷血屠殺，傑克因此誓言要找出兇手，為好朋友復仇。然而羅格來無影去無蹤，直到三年後才因為中國幫派老大（尊龍 飾）、日本黑幫領袖志郎（石橋凌Ryo Ishibashi 飾）搶地盤而重新露面.........<br />\n<br />\n3.2012年，美國經濟全面崩盤，導致失業率乃至犯罪率逐漸失控的情況下，一些富有權貴成立私人監獄來賺錢。其中一處則是「終結島」（Terminal Island）：一座距離內陸長達兩英里的海島監獄，不少死刑犯和終身監禁犯都被拘禁於此。典獄長克萊爾&middot;韓娜席通過網絡直播囚犯角鬥形式的生死決鬥來獲得更多利益，但因觀眾容易失去興趣，於是創立出囚犯互相靠賽車形式競爭的「亡命賽車」（Death Race）<br />\n<br />\n4.故事敘述一名職業殺手亞瑟&middot;畢夏（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）不但武藝高強、槍法神準，也心思縝密，手法乾淨俐落，在殺完人後會將死者看起來像意外、自殺或被另有人他殺的模樣，以避免警方的追捕。<br />\n劇情一開始，亞瑟聽信老闆迪恩（東尼&middot;高德溫飾）的謊話，誤以為恩師哈利（唐納&middot;蘇德蘭飾）背叛組織，奉命謀殺哈利，亞瑟誘導哈利到了他布置好的現場時，哈利放棄了抵抗，還幫助亞瑟做好自己被劫車的搶匪開槍打死的假象，所以亞瑟心懷愧疚..<br />\n<br />\n7 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=916c3352\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=275549ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d7f09a8896feb69d195a337c54f86efb046511","tid":1762130,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f20a4338ad1d45db01c5f1a9e60f233fe3df9b","tid":1762130,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd15465de2655b4a94a13ed12274bc239c25037","tid":1762130,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cdec67ed65001015d54273303c672790da0d04","tid":1762130,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af7f4e527349d9345aa3e65d88b25fef509a5c7","tid":1762130,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84448a2fb244e2bc70d4dbd86124b3aa